title.rendered: Paket CCTV Omniview 4 Channel Ultimate HDTVI

content.rendered: Tingkatkan sistem keamanan bangunan dengan memasang Omniview Paket CCTV Omniview 4 Channel Ultimate HDTVI. Kamera CCTV Omniview dapat menangkap gambar video bahkan dalam kondisi cahaya yang minim. Kamera Omniview Paket CCTV Omniview 4 Channel Ultimate HDTVI mempunyai spesifikasi, diantaranya: > Jumlah CCTV 4 Unit > Tipe CCTV CCTV Camera Omniview OMN-IAT200 > Resolusi CCTV 2 MP > Image Sensor 1/3” Sensor Resolution 960P Lens 3.6mm > Infrared Range IR Distance up to 30m IR > Tipe DVR CCTV DVR Omniview OMV-S04N > Fitur 04 Ch 1080N AHD DVR > Video Output Support VGA,HDMI HD Output > Audio In 4x Audio in / 1x Audio Out > Harddisk Support 1 HDD SATA up to 3 TB > Recording Resolution 4 Ch 1080N real-time > Jack DC 1 Paket > Adaptor 1 Paket > Konektor Drat 1 Paket
